saying he wanted to
create a bottom-up economy

00:40:35.550 --> 00:40:37.730
rather than a top-down
and had talked about

00:40:37.730 --> 00:40:39.150
changing benefits and taxes,

00:40:39.150 --> 00:40:41.970
that he was going to be
able to revolutionize

00:40:41.970 --> 00:40:45.010
American government the way Roosevelt did

